name: HackUs 101
description: This piece is part of the HackUs 10.14.10 portal series. It is a sister collection to HackUs 575 that takes place in a parallel universe. This digital artwork is in graphic formats of 2000 x 2000 pixels assembled in MP4 files, photographic and sonographic urban textures serve as a chaotic background for micro-fictions that invite you to peek into the cracks of the matrix.
